Interface NormalisedIntGraph

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Graph<V>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GraphImplLinearEdge, GraphImplLinearEdgeImportOptimised, GraphImplQuadratic, NormalisedIntGraphImplQuadratic

    public interface NormalisedIntGraph
extends java.lang.Cloneable
    Assumes that all nodes are normalised, i.e. their indices are [0..n-1]
    Author:
    sander
